00Z","msg":"老美想開你波就開你波 <br />\n黎緊老共都要準備定個八月十五<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:34:40.000Z","msg":"驚就驚大選對家食住好多美國佬憎trump<br />\n就全部政策打反trump方向，貿易戰都唔打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7028c2721844c62d2669a6aadc2dede138460fc","tid":1505991,"uid":206812,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:35:56.000Z","msg":"家母一路睇電視 見好多人爬山嘅時候<br />\n俾狗咬住個背囊走唔甩 咬到好傷好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以用師奶思想 建議大家<br />\n行山嘅時候 個書包入面裝水裝紙巾好喇<br />\n至於你啲身分證 或者電話其他重要嘢<br />\n有腰包就放腰包（要戴係面衫<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">裡面</span></span>啊懵佬）<br />\n無就好似呀婆咁 著條有袋/拉鍊嘅背心底衫喇<br />\n你知啲動物好鍾意咬住個袋唔放 唔俾你走<br />\n只要你個袋無重要嘢 就可以嚟一招<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">金蟬脫殼</span></span><br />\n<br />\n示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0JGmV6t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0JGmV6t.png&h=1aa75a82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小心個袋俾狗咬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506145\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506145</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c510f609f9814e4d8ded0979ff29f1de9b4a5ab1","tid":1505991,"uid":92442,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:41:55.000Z","msg":"攞油係左膠論述，無事實back up"},{"pid":"cfe99a7e46434834b1f23877df6551e836826d04","tid":1505991,"uid":9315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c6ae69f006463f2359cdf5c99c71f1e9d31ee46c","tid":1505991,"uid":101392,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8e1b56d8157cfa7641112e0d60fd3db5f459d151","tid":1505991,"uid":55375,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:41:25.000Z","msg":"快d係香港底下挖到油/稀土<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:01:17.000Z","msg":"其實香港個金融系統、司法系統仲珍貴過石油"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":